<subSubSection id="8294EDF0567CFFB4FF77FC3E5BC0FC64" pageId="9" pageNumber="124" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="CA31BE7B567CFFB4FF77FC3E5BC0FC64" blockId="9.[151,1437,908,1112]" pageId="9" pageNumber="124">
<emphasis id="F8FA6269567CFFB4FF77FC3E5967FC09" bold="true" box="[199,352,908,933]" pageId="9" pageNumber="124">Distribution.</emphasis>
The speCies is only known from its 
<typeStatus id="153500D9567CFFB4FD4DFC3F5B2AFC09" box="[765,813,909,933]" pageId="9" pageNumber="124">type</typeStatus>
loCality at National Natural Park Tatamá in the PaCifiC OCean slope of the Andean Cordillera OCCidental (
